have the potential to distinguish between periods of high connectivity that are\ngoverned by positive vs negative news in the market.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 21 Jul 2022 18:39:53 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 26 Jul 2022 16:56:40 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-07-27"}
