ing magnetic material, more information\nfrom other methods will be required to identify the correct physical mechanism\nby which a certain \"fingerprint\" in a FORC diagram is produced.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 22 Jul 2022 11:29:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-03-22"}
