s basin\nof attraction of the solutions of the sub-critical fast diffusion flow for\nradial initial data. In another application, we derive sharp quantitative\nstability of the Hardy-Sobolev-Maz'ya inequalities for the class of functions\nwhich are symmetric in the component of singularity.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 22 Jul 2022 11:57:08 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-07-25"}
