long with the corresponding statistical distributions, are derived and\ntheir accuracy systematically verified and validated against the finite element\nsimulation results of different Voronoi microstructures.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 22 Jul 2022 13:03:54 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-04-21"}
