ach as a promising path for the development of hollow-core fibers guiding\nat short wavelengths with loss that can potentially be orders of magnitude\nlower than the ones achievable with their silica-core counterparts.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 22 Jul 2022 13:57:07 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-03-22"}
